' CRON JOBS
' ============================================================

package "Background Jobs (Cron)" <<Frame>> #F1F8E9 {
    note as CronJobs
        **Every 5 minutes**
        → Deactivate expired boosts (Boost.isActive=false)

        **Every hour**
        → Precompute compatibility scores
          (500 users × 50 candidates → Redis)

        **Every 6 hours**
        → Update UserBehavior stats
          (totalMatches, likeToMatchRatio, daysActive)

        **Daily at midnight**
        → Cleanup analytics events > 90 days
    end note
}

